was added to this lovely garden
by
Forward 4 Work
(helping local people with disabilities into work)
on Rosie Day 12th May 2009.
These flowers have been planted in
loving memory of those we have lost and for the
wonderful work of nurses everywhere on
International Nurses Day."∆
